RDK PUPPET MODULES
Released under the terms of Apache2 licence

Official website:
https://github.com/rkhatibi/rdk-puppet-modules

A collection of modules for Puppet with the following targets:
- Multi OS support and easy integration of new OS
- Ubuntu 10.04, Fedora 14, RHEL 5-6, and CentOS 5-6 supported out of the box
- Adherence to Puppet modules standards
- Simple, easy to understand, stand alone modules for the beginning to intermediate Puppet user
- puppet-lint 0.1.4 approved
